name: Just Keep Floating
description: October 10 is the world mental health day awareness. This one is dedicated to all of us who are currently fighting inside our own head, trying to catch a breath engulfed by our own thoughts. Please remember that you can always scream for help, and that the lighthouse you see from afar is real. Don't let yourself drown yet. You're doing good. If you are too tired to swim, just keep floating.
